        <div class="project-card">

            <h2>Navix — Smart Travel Route Planner</h2>

            <p>
                A full-stack travel route planning application developed in a team of four 
                that computes optimized travel routes using graph algorithms and interactive 
                map visualization.
            </p>

            <h3>Features</h3>

            <ul>
                <li>Implemented Dijkstra’s Algorithm in C++ for optimal route computation</li>

                <li>Supported route optimization based on distance, time, and cost</li>

                <li>Integrated interactive map visualization using Leaflet and OpenStreetMap</li>

                <li>Added authentication and feedback storage using MongoDB</li>

                <li>Displayed alternative travel paths and graph-based route visualization</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Tech Stack</h3>

            <ul>
                <li>Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, EJS</li>

                <li>Backend: Node.js, Express.js</li>

                <li>Database: MongoDB</li>

                <li>Algorithms: C++, Dijkstra’s Algorithm, Graphs</li>

                <li>APIs: OpenStreetMap, OSRM</li>
            </ul>

